title: Various Artists - United Nations Of Messidor (1995)@flac
description:
An effective two-disc compilation of contemporary Latin music drawn from the catalog of German label Messidor Musik. 
The selections range from the highly traditional to the highly fused -- there are a lot of hybrid approaches on display here, giving rise to some spectacularly showy jazz-footed playing. 
Finger-popping, toe-tapping stuff, this, and very enjoyable throughout. (AMG)
